title: Shots Fired Outside UK Parliament in London - Reports
text:
Shots Fired Outside UK Parliament in London - Reports Â© AP Photo/ Kirsty Wigglesworth 0 437 4 0 Shots have reportedly been fired outside the UK Parliament in London; the building is currently on lockdown. 
Conflicting reports suggest that one or two people were shot by police outside the UK parliament in London. 
London Metropolitan police said they were aware of reports of the incident. 
According to media reports, there may be up to 12 injured near the UK parliament building.
